{"tid":165908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]兩工人維修電塔觸電　一人着火燒焦亡","createTime":"2017-03-21T16:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T17:25:45.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"539b61c1d0f8c2a54d2b7aa74590f39b351cf6a7","tid":165908,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170321/bkncn-20170321211927058-0321_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170321%2Fbkncn-20170321211927058-0321_05011_001.html&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=0baf6bb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170321/bkncn-20170321211927058-0321_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170321/photo/bkncn-20170321211927058-0321_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170321%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170321211927058-0321_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=a6909cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江蘇徐州市豐縣兩名工人，今日早上在鳳鳴公園西南角處的電塔上進行維修時，因不慎觸電，其中王姓工人當場着火燒死，另一名程姓工人則被送院搶救後，已無生命危險。目前，事故原因有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今早7時半左右，江蘇國豐電力工程有限公司兩名工人在維修電塔時，發生觸電意外。從網上流傳的短片和照片可見，一名工人觸電後倒吊在電塔上，上身起火，最後被燒焦，掛屍電塔之上。救援人員接報到場後，為受傷的工人急救。<br />\n<br />\n栗一燒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8199111ae952191ae712e5052277e458bd9687f","tid":165908,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"嘩，要你睇住隔離條友燒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}